  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: On Send Transaction and Request Transaction screens (Wallet, Unsigned tx or tx initiated from chat/DApp), in field Wallet Wallet amount overlaps the field and goes further to the edge of the screen\r\n![img_2938](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/31404591-c0c73c66-adfc-11e7-9f2b-3789b8528142.jpg)\r\n\r\n![img_2942](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/31404864-9179b866-adfd-11e7-9120-e69310dc8fec.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nIf amount can be fully shown then show as much as we can with … after amount and ETH, e.g “Main Wallet 12345678901.123456… ETH” \r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nAmount does not fit the field: text overlaps edge of the field border and goes behind the screen\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\nAccount should have enough ether, e.g. 10.123456789012345678\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open Wallet \r\n- Tap on Send and check the content of the Wallet field\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop\r\n* Operating System: Real device iPhone 5s",
